const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What does your monthly maid service cover?",
    answer: "Our Monthly Maid Service is designed to tackle the heavier chores that can build up over time. Each visit focuses on:\n\n• Kitchen & Bathrooms – Deep cleaning and sanitizing of sinks, toilets, tubs, showers, countertops, and appliance exteriors.\n• Dusting & Floors – Thorough dusting of furniture and surfaces, plus vacuuming and mopping throughout the home.\n• Hard-to-Reach Areas – Addressing spots like baseboards, vents, light fixtures, and other areas where dust and grime accumulate between visits.\n\nMonthly cleaning is a great option if you don’t need frequent upkeep but want your home refreshed and maintained with professional care."
  },
  {
    question: "Is monthly cleaning effective?",
    answer: "Yes—monthly cleaning can be very effective, especially if your home is low-traffic or you handle light upkeep between visits. Our team focuses on kitchens, bathrooms, and high-use areas, while also addressing dust, floors, and hard-to-reach buildup that may have accumulated since the last service.\n\nIf your household includes children, pets, or frequent guests, you may find that bi-monthly or weekly cleaning provides better consistency. During your free consultation, we’ll help you decide which schedule is the best fit for your lifestyle and home."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I add extra tasks to my monthly cleaning?",
    answer: "Absolutely. While our Monthly Maid Service is designed to cover kitchens, bathrooms, floors, and hard-to-reach areas, you can also customize each visit with optional add-ons, such as:\n\n• Cleaning inside the oven or refrigerator\n• Refreshing shutters and blinds\n• Changing linens\n• Extra detailing in specific rooms or spaces\n\nThis flexibility ensures your monthly cleaning not only resets your home but also addresses the chores that matter most to you."
  },
  {
    question: "Will the same person clean my home each month?",
    answer: "Yes. We do our best to assign the same trusted cleaner or team to your home for every visit, so you enjoy consistency, familiarity, and peace of mind. To ensure there are no interruptions, we also train a backup team on your home’s preferences. That way, if your regular cleaner is unavailable, you’ll still receive the same high-quality service and attention to detail you expect."
  },
  {
    question: "What if my home needs extra time?",
    answer: "If your home requires more time due to size, layout, or extra buildup between visits, we’ll let you know in advance and adjust the schedule and/or add personnel as needed. Our goal is to ensure your home receives the thorough care it deserves, without cutting corners.\n\nDuring your free consultation, we’ll walk through your home together to estimate the right amount of time and create a plan that fits your needs and budget. If additional tasks or time are requested beyond the standard monthly service, we’ll provide a clear quote for any add-on costs so there are no surprises."
  }
];



---

<BaseLayout>
